languages.text: "В лесах полно признаков порчи — измененные растения, взбешенные звери. Войдите под кроны — и вы сами заметите все это".

traits.locale_text: "В лесах полно признаков порчи — измененные растения, взбешенные звери. Войдите под кроны — и вы сами заметите все это".

languages.text: "The forests are teeming with signs of blight — distorted plants, deranged animals. Go into the trees and you will see it for yourself."

languages.text: “森林里充斥着枯萎的迹象——扭曲的植物、疯狂的动物。你去森林里亲眼看看就知道了。”
languages.original_text: "The forests are teeming with signs of blight — distorted plants, deranged animals. Go into the trees and you will see it for yourself."

traits.locale_text: “森林里充斥着枯萎的迹象——扭曲的植物、疯狂的动物。你去森林里亲眼看看就知道了。”

languages.text: 「森は死の気配で満ちている――ひずんだ植物に、錯乱した動物。木々に分け入ってその目で確かめるといい」
languages.original_text: "The forests are teeming with signs of blight — distorted plants, deranged animals. Go into the trees and you will see it for yourself."

traits.locale_text: 「森は死の気配で満ちている――ひずんだ植物に、錯乱した動物。木々に分け入ってその目で確かめるといい」

languages.text: "In den Wäldern gibt es überall Anzeichen von Krankheit – deformierte Pflanzen, verwirrte Tiere. Geht zu den Bäumen, dann seht Ihr es selbst."
languages.original_text: "The forests are teeming with signs of blight — distorted plants, deranged animals. Go into the trees and you will see it for yourself."

traits.locale_text: "In den Wäldern gibt es überall Anzeichen von Krankheit – deformierte Pflanzen, verwirrte Tiere. Geht zu den Bäumen, dann seht Ihr es selbst."

languages.text: « Les plantes déformées et les animaux dérangés sont les signes évidents d'une maladie. Il suffit d'aller dans la forêt pour le constater. »
languages.original_text: "The forests are teeming with signs of blight — distorted plants, deranged animals. Go into the trees and you will see it for yourself."

traits.locale_text: « Les plantes déformées et les animaux dérangés sont les signes évidents d'une maladie. Il suffit d'aller dans la forêt pour le constater. »

languages.text: «Los bosques rezuman las señales de la peste: plantas deformes, animales enloquecidos... Ve a la arboleda y compruébalo de primera mano».
languages.original_text: "The forests are teeming with signs of blight — distorted plants, deranged animals. Go into the trees and you will see it for yourself."

traits.locale_text: «Los bosques rezuman las señales de la peste: plantas deformes, animales enloquecidos... Ve a la arboleda y compruébalo de primera mano».

languages.text: "Ormanlar, hastalık işaretlerinden geçilmiyor. Bitkiler çarpılmış, şekilleri bozulmuş. Hayvanlarsa kudurmuş. Ağaçların arasına adım atarsan kendin de görürsün."
languages.original_text: "The forests are teeming with signs of blight — distorted plants, deranged animals. Go into the trees and you will see it for yourself."

traits.locale_text: "Ormanlar, afet işaretlerinden geçilmiyor: Bitkilerin şekli kaçmış, hayvanların dengesi kaymış. Ağaçların arasına adım atarsan kendin de görürsün."
